1. *Svinja* je požrtvovana žrtva. (The pig was a devoted sacrifice.)
2. *Svinje* su se približile ugledu. (The pigs approached the respect.)
3. *Svinjom* je vlasnik obavio mnoge poslove. (The owner accomplished many tasks with the pig.)
4. *Svinju* je čuvala majka. (The mother guarded the pig.)
5. *Svinji* je pružena velika dobrota. (Great kindness was shown to the pig.)
6. *Svinja* je bila vrlo hrabra. (The pig was very brave.)